Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No… Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got the same Sharingan\Nas Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who’d believe a kid like you to\Nhave the Nine-Tailed Fox in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that guy know\Nabout the Nine-Tailed Fox?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, you will come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Chidori!\NBrother vs. Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is…close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when school’s over,\Nhelp me train for a Shuriken Jutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m busy… Have father teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re better at Shuriken Jutsu,\NElder Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always treat me\Nlike a pest, Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me Sasuke…\NSome other time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have time to\Npay attention to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re always jabbing my forehead\Nand saying "Forgive me, Sasuke."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also say "not today,"\Nbut there's never a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn’t Elder Brother\Npay any attention to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy’s a little strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s the type that doesn’t really like\Nto become intimate with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am his father and\Nstill I can’t read that boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boxed lunch, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re worried about doing\NShuriken Jutsu practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will watch you when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re not practices,\Nthey’re training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke, are you on\Nyour way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Itachi earlier on.\NHe’s really become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s already a top-notch Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He graduated at the head of his class\Nat the Academy at the age of seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attained Chunin level\Nat the age of ten, didn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became adept at using\NSharingan at the age of eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is truly\Nthe pride of the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\Nhow old are you now, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the same age as\Nwhen Elder Brother graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke, both you and Itachi\Ncome from the same Uchiha clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pedigree of\Nthe Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be an amazing\NShinobi just like Itachi one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I come from the same Uchiha clan\Nas Elder Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t lose to Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m pretty late…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the feeling\Nthere was someone there…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights are out.\NEven though it’s not time for bed…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle… Auntie…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father… Mother…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s somebody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother!\NFather and Mother are…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world would do\Nsomething like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother… What are you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing,\NElder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish little brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make me see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you, Elder Brother…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie! Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t kill Father and Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you…? Elder Brother…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To measure my abilities…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Measure your abilities…?\NJust for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that…\Nyou killed them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is of great importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t talk rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t kill me…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not even worth killing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish little brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to kill me, begrudge me!\NHate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And keep on surviving in\Nthat unsightly manner…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just continue fleeing and fleeing\Nand hang onto your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go outside…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys aren’t just anybody…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi, it’ll be a pain in the neck\Nif this kid moves around and…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I better chop off\Na leg just in case…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi…Uchiha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as Sasuke…\NAn Uchiha…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…Sharingan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover,\Nhe resembles you a lot…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that the entire Uchiha clan\Nhad been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi Uchiha…I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must kill one certain man\Nwithout fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My elder brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I couldn’t die…\Nwithout killing him, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the guy that Sasuke\Nwas saying …
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man he wanted to kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just as you said…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I held a grudge against you\Nand hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the singular purpose of\Nkilling you, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have lived my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chidori…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe that Sasuke’s Jutsu\Nwas so easily thwarted…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn’t look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chakra permeates the air…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Nine-Tailed Fox Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Summo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…? I can’t feel the Chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Darn! Why is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sword Shark Skin\Nhas the ability to…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cut through and eat Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pain in the butt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the kid moves around\Nand uses Jutsu like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before these legs…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I chop off these arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn’t it emerge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s pointless…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just don’t know me much,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man Jiraiya does not fall victim\Nto any woman’s allurement,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but rather his forte is\Nwinning women’s affection!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not made to blindly follow after\Na woman’s feminine charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to my level,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,women yelp with delight\Nat my sex appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cycle of hardship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside, we were crying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one thing we won't give up\Nis the dream we've chosen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secondary role,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a role in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reaching for that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us stay centered,\Nlet us stay true
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe hung on without giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe kept coming back up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe believed and dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over,\Nwe've seen fools\
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, don’t help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…Sasuke is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:23:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your duty to watch\Nthrough this battle, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This represents everything that\Nhe has been carrying up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “Hate Among the Uchihas:\NThe Last of the Clan!”
